other_tests.findings: Slightly thickened collagen bundles within the dermis; thickened elastic fibers in the mid to deep reticular dermis consistent with a connective tissue nevus.

other_tests.changes_over_time: New attacks of eczematous eruption occurred with multiple drugs over a 2-year follow-up.

other_tests.findings: Positive reactions with most of the suspected drugs; control testing was negative for hydroxyzine and pseudoephedrine.
other_tests.changes_over_time: No new attack has occurred since 2007.
